og`.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Review/cherry-pick the preserved candidate from the branch above, especially the `preSettled()` addition in `Spring_rabbitmq_clientTest.java`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.springframework.amqp:spring-rabbitmq-client:4.1.0-M2` from that candidate to confirm the green result.\n3. Investigate why metrics/artifact capture recorded `generated_loc: 0` and `artifacts: None` despite the passing candidate, and rerun or repair that reporting step."}}
